but there are no event handlers to process them</doc></exception><value><value><root><base><xml src="index.xml"><cmti name="Equeue" src="/home/dsheets/.opam/doc/build/ocamlnet.3.7.7/src/equeue/equeue.cmti" digest="207ed21b384dd4f4ad91bce8a449f64c"/></xml></base>Equeue</root>create</value><doc>Creates a new event system that has an event source, but is
